Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,================== EDCN ==================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在这烟波浩翰的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}万千世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:41.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你我二人是否相遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:51.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然不会轻易相信命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只是希望你我能同见一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:05.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论明天迎来的是泪眼还是欢颜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}都不合适后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:17.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因为有你陪伴在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:24.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以我才能坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也许是徒绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:32.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就是绕远路又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}路依旧延绵不尽
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,================== EDJP ==================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}色とりどりの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:37.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界で偶然に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:41.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}出会ってしまったの？　二人は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:51.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}運命なんて簡単に信じれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}おんなじ夢　見ていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:05.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}泣き顔も笑顔も　やって来る明日に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}後悔に似合わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:17.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:24.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}強い気持ちでいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ジグザグかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:32.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ジグザグでもいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:37.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\fsp0}forever and ever with you
